this is a generall approch to solve lot of backtracking question make a function and pass parameter as question and answer . build answer while going up.
**CODE:**
```
class Solution {
    public List<List<String>> partition(String s) {
        result=new ArrayList<>();
        partitionHelper(s,new ArrayList<>());
        return result;
    }
    private List<List<String>> result;

    private boolean isPalindrome(String str){
        int low=0 , high=str.length()-1;

        while(low<high){
            if(str.charAt(low)!=str.charAt(high)) return false;
            low++;
            high--;
        }
        return true;
    }

    private void partitionHelper(String ques,List<String> ans){
        if(ques.length()==0){
            result.add(new ArrayList<>(ans));
            return;
        }

        for(int i=0;i<ques.length();i++){
            String prefix=ques.substring(0,i+1);
            if(isPalindrome(prefix)){
          String ros=ques.substring(i+1); //ros: rest of string
                ans.add(prefix);
                partitionHelper(ros,ans);
                ans.remove(ans.size()-1);
            }
        }
    }
}
```

