# Intuition
Power of 2 does not have more than a single bit in their binary form

# Approach
1. if n is 0 or negative *return false.*
2. else just use the ***__builtin_popcount*** to calculate the number of bits in the number.
3. return *true* if bit count is 1 , *else false*

# Code
```
class Solution {
public:
    bool isPowerOfTwo(int n) {
        //power of two do not have no more than a single bit in them

        if(n <= 0)
            return false;

        int bits = __builtin_popcount(n);

        return bits == 1;

    }
};
```

