If you are here, try implementing an iterative solution without converting into char array. It improves memory utilization from linear to constant.
```
class Solution {
    public boolean isValidSerialization(String preorder) {
        String[] nodes = preorder.split(",");
        final String _hash = "#";

        int count = 1;
        for(String n : nodes) {
            count--;
            if(count < 0)
                return false;
            if(!n.equals(_hash))
                count += 2;
        }

        return count == 0;
    }
}
```

